@matthewroach This is an issue with the video component/powa player.  Powa calculates their padding to two decimal places.  And our util/formatPowaVideEmbed just uses the calculated value.  So when you request a 16/9 ratio, you get 0.5625 and powa uses a padding of 5.62% which causes a discrepancy.  I can fix the util function to floor the value (I also see there is an issue with aspect-ratio v. aspectratio this may actually be the real issue :p)
